task.summary: Default task
- dart template working with raw text - handles expressions and regexs properly - injects regex support into annotation strings
basics of the run configurations starting to work

- cleanup of Runner configurations - ensure the forms are working correctly for all variations of tests - detect flutter packages in projects and that tests are in the correct location for the appropriate tests. - Allow for override of observatory port
- now able to run cucumber test apps, does not support flutter methods yet.

- class level support - dynamic instance injection - declared shared instances across whole run - support both old and new styles
todo: - json style reporting required for IDEA - testing for single scenario run override - allow forced failure when stepdefs are missing

Support cuke3 expressions
This adds cucumber3 expression support, and also ensures that for classes at least, the parameters are being cast to a string if they are decoded as not a string.
- matching for dherkin3 packages - fixing the snippet generator so it generates cuke3 expression syntax by default.
- navigate to the correct method when it has been created
- add details to the readme to cover what is new in dherkin3 - add support for before and after hooks
- correctly saving the dart file that is being used - correctly discovering Flutter as per code pulled from the Flutter IDEA Plugin.
- minor code cleanup
- more minor cleanup, discovery of how message filters are working
- extraction of text output out of core code into separate basic formatter
variable replacement working properly and as expected in a cucumber implementation.

- proper support for strings in expressions for example/outline based replacement (i.e. "<col>") - support for negative integers in expressions - fixed per session injection where outline is used for cucumber and examples exist, session state was bleeding across examples
- cleaned up scenario printing so we don't get two scenario passed/fails
- basic test formatting is now working and the tests are running. - failure isn't working and coming back, and there is no debugging.
- failure now working as we are waiting for the correct future - formatter now outputting stack trace as expected - snippet recognizing parameterized examples for ints and floats in IDE
- properly support hotreload for flutter apps and ignore dart style testing with expects as we aren't using it with cucumber.
- cleaned up a lot of common code in producers - rerunning from test menu now works and creates profiles without overwriting the original one it was copied from
- allow dart feature files to be selected from files menu
created program runner to allow for debugging
- support for the token now required when running the app already
- jump to source in IDEA needs absolute paths
renamed project readying for release
update the pubspec

renaming all the code base to ogurets
support beforerun and afterun annotations
Changes to allow for auto-generation of necessary run config files.
Documentation changes
Fix issue with IDEA not picking up changed file.
